name: RobloxGamePicker
0:
”Alexa, open roblox game picker”
”Alexa, start roblox game picker”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: roblox game picker
des: When you don't know what game to play on Roblox or just wanting to try something new, let Alexa choose a game for you. Alexa picks a random game from a list and chooses for you. Say "Alexa, stop" to stop the skill. Your requests aren't shared with me (the skill developer)
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
